-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/four-tet">Four Tet</a>分享了新专辑《Three》的详细信息，并发布了新单曲《Daydream Repeat》。看看下面。</p><p>这张即将推出的专辑将包含八首歌曲，标志着这位英国制作人近四年来的第一张完整专辑——继 2020 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/four-tet-sixteen-oceans-music-to-listen-to-self-isolation-coronavirus-covid-19-2630582">《十六大洋》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-releases-two-new-albums-parallel-871-2845515">《871》和《平行》</a>之后。</p><p>该专辑预计于 3 月 15 日上市，并将通过 Four Tet（真名 Kieran Hebden）自己的唱片公司 Text Records 发行。</p><p>在 Bleep 上宣布新项目时，Hebden 还分享了即将推出的《Three》曲目列表，并确认其中将收录他上个月发布的上一首单曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-shares-immersive-new-single-loved-3568641">《Loved》</a> ，以及他去年春天推出的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-new-track-three-drums-3436311">《Three Drums》</a> 。</p><p> 《Three》现已<a href="https://www.roughtrade.com/en-us/product/four-tet/three-8?cjdata=MXxZfDB8WXww&amp;utm_source=CJ&amp;cjevent=cf7c4d98cc1511ee8101005a0a18b8f8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">开放预订</a>，您可以查看由杰森·埃文斯 (Jason Evans) 和马修·库珀 (Matthew Cooper) 设计的专辑封面以及下面的曲目列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3588044" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3588044" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3588044" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000.jpg" alt="四春节的“三”专辑封面" width="2000" height="2011" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-400x402.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-800x804.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-696x700.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-1392x1400.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Four-Tet-Three@2000x2000-1068x1074.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3588044" class="wp-caption-text">四春节的“三”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“三”的曲目列表是：</strong></h2><p> <strong>1.“爱”</strong><br /> <strong>2.“滑过一切”</strong><br /> <strong>3.“风暴水晶”</strong><br /> <strong>4.“白日梦重复”</strong><br /> <strong>5.“滑冰者”</strong><br /> <strong>6.《31 绽放》</strong><br /> <strong>7.《那么蓝》</strong><br /> <strong>8.《三鼓》</strong></p><p>除了分享新专辑的消息外，Hebden 还以新单曲《Daydream Repeat》的形式发布了这张 LP 的最新试听版。</p><p>这首歌的长度只有六分钟多一点，以快节奏的节拍为核心，辅以空灵的钢琴旋律，逐渐上升到前景。下面请听一下。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="白日梦重复" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bKaRxvxeUzs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他春节四月新闻中，这位英国制片人已被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bonnaroo-2024-post-malone-red-hot-chili-peppers-fred-again-lead-line-up-2-3568074">宣布为今年 Bonnaroo 的演出名单之一</a>。</p><p>已宣布将于 6 月 13 日至 16 日演出的其他演员包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/maggie-rogers">Maggie Rogers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dominic-fike">Dominic Fike</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzy-mcalpine">Lizzy McAlpine</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/interpol">Interpol</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/parcels">Parcels</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">Idles</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/brittany-howard">Brittany Howard</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jason-isbell">Jason Isbell and the 400 Unit</a> 、Fisher 和更多的。</p><p>去年，Hebden<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fred-again">再次</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a>和 Fred 联手，结束了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/coachella">Coachella 音乐节</a>的第二个周末。周日，他们在主舞台上接替了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blink-182">Blink-182</a>之后的“TBA”时段，此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/frank-ocean-blink-182-coachella-weekend-2-3432864">Frank Ocean 在音乐节前夕因腿部骨折，按照医生的指示退出了 Coachella Weekend 2</a> 。</p><p>此前，三人曾在纽约麦迪逊广场花园同台演出， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/skrillex-fred-again-four-tet-announce-surprise-show-new-york-3399251">惊喜演出几分钟之内就被抢购一空</a>。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/skrillex-live-in-new-york-city-a-once-in-a-lifetime-rave-at-the-garden-3401021">该剧的四星评论</a>中表示：“当舞曲从花园的墙壁上弹起时，不仅由于霓虹灯的快速闪烁，场地呈现出不同的色调，而且能量也不同了。过道里的粉丝挤满了人，但尽管场地拥挤，每个人都同步跳舞，这证明了成千上万的狂欢者之间的联系不仅仅是他们快速购买门票的能力。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/four-tet-announces-new-album-three-with-the-track-daydream-repeat-3588034">四月春节后宣布新专辑《Three》中的歌曲《Daydream Repeat》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
